- `KeyMsg(KeyEvent)` - Handle text input and navigation
- `InsertChar(char)` - Insert character at cursor
- `InsertString(String)` - Insert/paste text
- `DeleteChar` - Backspace
- `DeleteCharForward` - Delete key
- `DeleteWord` - Delete word backward
- `DeleteToEnd` - Delete from cursor to end
- `DeleteToStart` - Delete from start to cursor
- `MoveCursor(Direction)` - Left/right/home/end
- `SetValue(String)` - Replace all text
- `Focus` / `Blur` - Focus state
- `CursorBlink` - Toggle cursor visibility
- `SetEchoMode(EchoMode)` - Normal/password/none

### view() -> String
- Render text with cursor
- Apply echo mode (show asterisks for password)
- Show placeholder if empty
- Apply prompt prefix

